程序包 cn.domob.android.ads

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    AdEventListener
    Call method "setAdEventListener" of a instance of DomobAdView to set event listener.
    AdListener
    An interface for listening Domob banner ads.
    FeedsAdListener  
    InterstitialAdListener
    An interface for listening Domob interstitial ads.
    RTSplashAdListener
    An interface for listening Domob real time splash ads.
    SplashAdListener
    An interface for listening Domob splash ads.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    AdManager
    A class for managing Domob ads.
    AdView
    A class for invoking Domob banner ads.
    FeedsAdView
    A class for invoking Domob Feeds ads.
    InterstitialAd
    A class for invoking Domob interstitial ads.
    RTSplashAd
    A class for invoking Domob real time splash ads.
    SplashAd
    A class for invoking Domob splash ads.
    Updater
    A class for reminding update.

    InterstitialAd.BorderType
